A simple technique is described that facilitates a proper procedure of venous zzso anastomosis during neurosurgical zzso This zzso which consists of insertion of a zzso tube in the vein during zzso results in easier handling and proper apposition of the zzso resulting in an improved quality of the zzso The technique was successfully applied in a patient after zzso meningioma zzso and the patency of the cortical vein was confirmed postoperatively on magnetic resonance zzso 
